  "whatsapp_greeting": "\ud83d\udc4b Hey! I'm your AI Trading Coach with full access to your data including auto-synced broker accounts AND real-time Market Cause Engine intelligence.\n\nI can:\n\ud83d\udcca Analyze trades from all your connected brokers\n\ud83e\udde0 Explain market movements with causality analysis (not just indicators)\n\ud83c\udfaf Tell you if current market conditions favor YOUR trading style\n\u26a0\ufe0f Monitor prop firm compliance in real-time\n\ud83d\udca1 Identify your optimal market regimes (RISK-ON, NEUTRAL, etc.)\n\ud83d\udd04 Analyze trade copying performance\n\ud83d\udcc8 Correlate your trades with market regimes and scores\n\nWhat would you like to work on today?"
